name: Malakili (V)
Lore: 'Corellian. Worked for Circus Horrificus. Disapproves of Jabba''s treatment of the rancor. Plotting with Lady Valarian to steal the immense beast away from Jabba''s palace.',
Text: 'Deploys -4 on Tatooine. Rancors may deploy here (even if Malakili is not the only character, habitat permitting), are defense value +4 here, and may not attack Malakili. During your deploy phase, may deploy one Rancor here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
